name: First pinnacle of SPACESHIP_COUPLES
description:
SPACESHIP_COUPLES: 2 entities emerging to validate their existence despite the absence of humakind.

The SPACESHIP_COUPLES were originally to be taken off digital into analogue so I offset-printed them and experimented with overlay. I exaggerated it, put them again into digital with even more layers. 

See the animated SPACESHIP_COUPLES on OpenSea: opensea.io/collection/spaceship-couples
